{"tid":1154498,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警員危站】警員控訴被同僚欺凌　危站於坪洲警崗三樓簷篷對峙","createTime":"2019-05-14T10:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T10:43:29.000Z","uid":6497,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9f27b2fac033a82c0681a26194e8daef7f4ee7","tid":1154498,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2795347/org/afc188472119ab3fef957d86b097bef3.png/8TR3-DPtjG8WjZXgJTt4RJeVU6VlUyf2Pmtzoz5rc6M?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2795347%2Forg%2Fafc188472119ab3fef957d86b097bef3.png%2F8TR3-DPtjG8WjZXgJTt4RJeVU6VlUyf2Pmtzoz5rc6M%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=89c980e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今（14日）下午5時許，一名男子在坪洲警崗三樓簷篷危站，警方及消防到場了解。由於事主危站的位置在橫巷，消防員未能張開氣墊。警方正安排談判專家到場。據了解，危站男子為一名姓郭警員，駐守坪洲一年多，在坪洲警崗內工作。他聲稱被同事欺凌，而上司包庇同事，於是危站控訴。"},{"pid":"cea10fc52e7b74c0b585b949341fb9ba8a484e4d","tid":1154498,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e469da12c98fd6c87b4c20b93a79acea5d4c64","tid":1154498,"uid":196092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:42:08.000Z","msg":"呀sir蝦人唔洗你教"},{"pid":"c9c6c23cce9d3232131b861d4166b46e6391f1e2","tid":1154498,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔辭職咁佢過唔過到bar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}